# Gateway Command Template
#
# This template generates the gateway command markdown file.
# Placeholders use {{placeholder}} syntax and are replaced at generation time.
#
# Execution semantics: .hiivmind/blueprint/execution-guide.md

---
name: {{plugin_name}}
description: >
  Unified entry point for {{plugin_name}} operations - describe what you need
  in natural language or select from the menu.
arguments:
  - name: request
    description: What you want to do (optional - shows menu if omitted)
    required: false
---

## Usage

```
/{{plugin_name}}                    # Show interactive menu
/{{plugin_name}} [request]          # Route by natural language intent
/{{plugin_name}} --help             # Show full help
/{{plugin_name}} [flags] [request]  # With runtime flags
```

{{#if_runtime_flags}}
## Runtime Flags

Flags modify workflow execution. Per-invocation only (reset for each command).

| Flag | Effect |
|------|--------|
| `--verbose`, `-v` | Show all node details (level: verbose) |
| `--quiet`, `-q` | Only prompts and final result (level: quiet) |
| `--debug` | Full state dumps (level: debug) |
| `--no-log` | Disable file logging |
| `--no-display` | Silent mode (no terminal output) |
| `--ci` | CI mode: GitHub annotations |

